(15, '2013-04-09 04:41:26', 'Farewell Ceremony DUETCS Committee 2012(09-04-2013)', 'DUET Computer Society is going to arrange farewell ceremony for DUETCS Committee 2012&nbsp;on 9th April 2013. All of you are cordially invited.&nbsp;<br /><br />Chief Guest: <br />Dr. Md. Nasim Akhter<br />Associate Professor &amp; Head, Dept. of CSE and Chief Patron, DUET CS<br /><br />Special Guest:<strong><br /></strong>Dr. Mohammod Abul Kashem<br />Associate Professor, Dept. of CSE<br /><br />Chaired By:<br />Md. Mahbub Alam<br />Lecturer, Dept. of CSE and Moderator, DUET CS<br /><br />'),
(16, '2013-05-06 10:08:04', 'General Meeting of DUETCS (07/05/2013)', 'We are announcing to all members of DUET Computer Society that our general meeting of Computer Society will be held on Tuesday, 07/05/2013, our moderator will be attend on this meeting.<br /><br />All of the DUET Computer Society Members are invited to join this meeting and make this successful for us.<br /><br />Place: Room No. 418(Academic Building), DUET, Gazipur.<br />Time: 1.45pm<br />'),
